Player performance is determined based on the following rules: 
- 'Below Average': total yards < 100, total touchdowns < 1, or total defensive stats < 20; 
- 'Average': total yards is between 100 and 200, total touchdowns is between 1 and 2, or total defensive stats is between 20 and 50; 
- 'Above Average': total yards > 200, total touchdowns > 2, or total defensive stats > 50; 
- Player status is 'New Player' if games played < 15, 'Needs Improvement' if average score < 80 or any performance is 'Below Average', 'Performing Well' if any performance is 'Above Average', and 'Average' otherwise.
